{"tid":569161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔信樓價再升20年！】 賣自住樓等樓價冧！","createTime":"2018-02-22T12:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T00:10:39.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b4981bb382e5b019db69863825c6b48cf384d5a0","tid":569161,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T12:25:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/22/202509_d6907ce7772254f7fe7cc0b1c8d3c3ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F22%2F202509_d6907ce7772254f7fe7cc0b1c8d3c3ee.png&h=401ae87f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d909186cbe7c6f2e618cf56a92784fafb5c0e62","tid":569161,"uid":93986,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T12:32:23.000Z","msg":"一樣野印花稅<br />\n<br />\n而家乾升其中一個原因就係放盤供應小，冇人肯賣樓，因為再買一層收租樓成本要多15%稅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但你想佢跌？政府一取消印花稅，樓市又gogogo <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖中既撚樣呢幾年見唔少（好多重要係專業人士），全部而家都後悔不得了。（早3年個個話加息，歐洲經濟唔好，英國脫歐）"},{"pid":"94531f6553b26e400df8d394c3d896236d193f22","tid":569161,"uid":93986,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T12:34:00.000Z","msg":"想市跌唔難，港人要先學識訓街<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無錯<br />\n<br />\n就係訓街"},{"pid":"3aae3825a0f53618c7cf1a9faa7185f02d293da3","tid":569161,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T12:37:52.000Z","msg":"原本要買樓既需求已經大，起新樓又小<br />\n2手放盤又小，根本唔會降低價值。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跌可能會，但跌既意思係經濟整體唔好，可能天災人禍，個個都冇錢或手緊（包括你），咪會冇人接貨。<br />\n買唔到既依舊買唔到，而家唔想買既依舊唔想買"},{"pid":"c611e830ea0ac86f5fdf76edecfa62aaf81c17be","tid":569161,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94531f6553b26e400df8d394c3d896236d193f22","tid":569161,"uid":93986,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T12:34:00.000Z","msg":"想市跌唔難，港人要先學識訓街<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無錯<br />\n<br />\n就係訓街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T12:39:51.000Z","msg":"降低買樓既需求，培養訓街習慣，房屋回到供求平衡，房價自然合理。"},{"pid":"889e87